WEBVTT

00:06:27.910 --> 00:06:31.966
where I thought,
"I can't go back to this job."

00:06:31.990 --> 00:06:35.389
I felt like I was wasting time,
like I was wasting my life.

00:06:35.824 --> 00:06:39.515
AG: I'm all for working in a career
that's a perfect fit for your passion.

00:06:39.539 --> 00:06:42.541
But hunting for that perfect fit
can be a real source of agony.

00:06:43.188 --> 00:06:45.347
There's evidence
that searching for a calling

00:06:45.371 --> 00:06:49.676
leaves college students feeling
indecisive, uncomfortable and confused.

00:06:50.300 --> 00:06:52.131
You might be one of the fortunate few

00:06:52.155 --> 00:06:54.958
to quickly find a career outlet
for your passion.

00:06:55.395 --> 00:06:58.276
Everyone else just flounders
around feeling lost.

00:06:58.919 --> 00:07:02.119
Maria finally ended up
working as a TV producer for two years.